<!-- src/templates/emails/driver-license-expiring.hbs -->
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>Driver License Expiration Warning</title>
		<style>
			body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color:
			#333; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container { max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; } .header { background-color:
			#ff9800; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: white; } .content
			{ padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; } .button { display:
			inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #4a86e8; color:
			white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;
			font-weight: bold; } .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;
			font-size: 12px; color: #777; } .warning-box { background-color:
			#fff3e0; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px;
			border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; } .license-list { margin: 15px 0; }
			.license-item { margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px;
			border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header">
				<h1>Driver License Expiration Warning</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="content">
				<p>Hello {{name}},</p>
				<p>This is an important notification regarding upcoming driver
					license expirations for your fleet. The following driver
					licenses will expire soon and require your attention:</p>

				<div class="warning-box">
					<h3>Licenses Expiring Soon:</h3>
					<div class="license-list">
						{{#each expiringLicenses}}
							<div class="license-item">
								<p><strong>Driver:</strong>
									{{this.driverName}}
									(ID:
									{{this.driverId}})</p>
								<p><strong>License Number:</strong>
									{{this.licenseNumber}}</p>
								<p><strong>License Type:</strong>
									{{this.licenseType}}</p>
								<p><strong>Expiry Date:</strong>
									{{this.expiryDate}}</p>
								<p><strong>Days Remaining:</strong>
									{{this.daysRemaining}}</p>
								<p><strong>Assigned Vehicle:</strong>
									{{this.assignedVehicle}}</p>
							</div>
						{{/each}}
					</div>
				</div>

				<p>Please ensure that these drivers renew their licenses before
					expiration. Driving with an expired license can result in:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Legal penalties for both the driver and your company</li>
					<li>Insurance coverage issues in case of accidents</li>
					<li>Regulatory compliance violations</li>
					<li>Potential suspension of your vehicle operations</li>
				</ul>

				<div style="text-align: center;">
					<a href="{{driversUrl}}" class="button">Manage Drivers</a>
				</div>

				<p>Once the licenses have been renewed, please update the
					information in your
					{{appName}}
					account to maintain accurate records.</p>

				<p>Best regards,<br />The {{appName}} Team</p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer">
				<p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
				<p>{{companyAddress}}</p>
				<p><a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Manage notification preferences</a></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>